PICSHARE - A microserviced containerized Application with DB postgres using prisma and neon using nest js with valid DTO and used gits for daily commits. User can create groups , it become admin of that group , user can send friend request , other user can accept the friend request so become part of that group


USING NX - multi service
npx create-nx-workspace@latest pixshare --preset=nest
nx generate @nrwl/nest:app user
nx generate @nrwl/nest:app group
Running command - npx nx serve user


prisma -
npx prisma migrate dev --name update-schema --create-only
npx prisma migrate dev
npx prisma db push

Database mapping
TABLE --------------
1) user
2) group
3) usergroupmapping

User - 
id
name 
username 
image

group -
id
name
admin_user
admin_name

usergroupmapping - 
id
userid
groupid